trans-unit.source: Defines the events relevant to <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 定义与 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 对象相关的事件。

trans-unit.source: The implementing object defines the context on which these events occur.
trans-unit.target: 实现对象可定义这些事件发生的上下文。

trans-unit.source: The sender in all events should be the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject> instance related to the event.
trans-unit.target: 中的所有事件的发送方应<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject>与事件相关的实例。

trans-unit.source: Occurs after you deploy an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在部署 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例后发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs after you begin deploying an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在开始部署 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例后发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you add a new <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在添加新 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you dispose an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在释放新 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you initialize an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you request context menu items from an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在请求 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例的上下文菜单项时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you rename an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在重命名 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you query an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance for its properties.
trans-unit.target: 在查询 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例的属性时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you change a project property value in an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例中更改项目属性值时发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs when you remove an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 在删除 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject" /> 实例时发生。
